This assertion is probably flaky as there is no guarantee that after `System.gc()` any actually leaked object will see its weak ref cleared. 

I think awaitility can help here:

```java
await().atMost(5, TimeUnit.SECONDS).until(() ->
{
    System.gc();
    pool.sweep();
    return pool.size();
}, is(2));
```
